  "keyFeatures": [
    "Lightweight 2D game engine built on Raylib",
    "Integrated Dear ImGui editor with WYSIWYG workflow",
    "Component-based design using 'Variants' with runtime reflection (RTTR)",
    "Live runtime property editing from the editor",
    "Query API for entity-component access (get, read, find_all, for_each, etc.)",
    "SET_CALLBACK macro for reactive property changes",
    "Clang-based preparser for automatic RTTR code generation",
    "Tracy profiling integration",
    "ImGui Test Engine for automated smoke tests",
    "Cross-platform build system via Premake5",
    "Editor-engine communication over ZeroMQ"
  ],
